pageProduct.name: The Natural Confectionery Co. Party Mix 180g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

The Natural Confectionery Co. Party Mix... let's party!

Let's Party! The Natural Confectionery Co. Party Mix are a party for your taste buds. Aussie Made and packed full of deliciousness, with no artificial colours, no artificial flavours, no GMOs and no artificial sweeteners.

Dig in and give your taste buds a reason to celebrate! Our yummy flavours: Juicy Orange, Wild Blackcurrant, Luscious Raspberry, Tangy Lemon, Succulent Strawberry and Cream, Crisp Apple, Creamy Milk

Contains Wheat.

Product Claims: No artificial colours, flavours and sweetener. No high fructose corn syrup and no GMO.

Size: 180g

Flavour: Juicy Orange, Wild Blackcurrant, Delectable Smooth Banana, Luscious Raspberry, Tangy Lemon, Succulent Strawberry and Cream, Crisp Apple, Creamy Milk.

Serving Size: 25g (Approx. 3-4 pieces)

Servings Per Pack: 7.2

Warnings

Not all varieties of party mix may be contained in this pack.

Ingredients

Glucose Syrup (from Wheat and Corn), Cane Sugar, Thickener (Acid Modified Wheat Starch), Gelatine, Food Acid (Citric), Fruit Juice Concentrate, Natural Food Colours (Anthocyanins, Black Carrot, Grape Skin Extract, Spirulina, Paprika Oleoresin, Turmeric), Glazing Agent (Vegetable Oil, Carnauba Wax).

Contains: Wheat

Allergen Contains: Wheat

Directions

Please store in cool, dry conditions.

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

In Australia, this packaging is recyclable through the REDcycle Program. Visit www.redcycle.net.au Recycle Wrap. Return to Store. arl.org.au

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
